title: GetBACnetDateRangeProperty (Method)
text:
METHOD GetBACnetDateRangeProperty :
BACnetDateRange
Returns the BACnet-DateRange-Value OF the specified PROPERTY (propID) OF THIS BACnet-Object as a BACnetDateRange STRUCT.
The used functions are no client, meaning, that the access of the property is not restricted by write or read access restrictions.

rows.Name: propID
rows.Comment: The ID of the property to get.
